column5: Plan to come through Int'l Falls going into Canada this Saturday morning (bad idea, I know.) How long can I expect to wait? We hope to hit it by 8:00 or 9:00. BB
We went through this past weekend at 4:30 a.m...zero wait. We heard at 8:00 a.m. the wait was 4 hours. Good luck with it.
Hi. the time goes by fast when your trying to collect the money to pay those blood sucking paper mill folks the bridge toll and to pick up your duty free booze.
are they usually backed up on Friday mornings...or is it just luck of the draw
